16. Foreign Key Relation Example

Subjects with Department:

SELECT s.id, s.name, sem.semester_number, d.name
FROM public.timetable_app_subject s
JOIN public.timetable_app_semester sem
ON s.semester_id = sem.id
JOIN public.timetable_app_department d
ON sem.department_id = d.id;
