23. Find Duplicate Rows
SELECT name, COUNT(*)
FROM public.timetable_app_department
GROUP BY name
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
24. Delete Duplicate Rows
DELETE FROM public.timetable_app_department a
USING public.timetable_app_department b
WHERE a.id < b.id
AND a.name = b.name;
25. Full Reset + Seed Workflow
python manage.py flush
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py seed